Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:07.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,受了一次挫折你就越来越懦弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:13.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,的确 辉夜大小姐曾度过的暑假都是悲惨的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:18.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这次暑假你一次都没见到白银会长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:23.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,从长远来看 却可以说是最佳选择
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:29.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,无法见面的时间将培育爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:33.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长现在和辉夜大小姐是同样的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:38.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都思念得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:41.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都掰着手指数着还有多久暑假才能结束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:49.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在此情此景下 要是能和辉夜大小姐来一场命运的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:53.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那么他迄今为止积攒下来的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:57.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就会被一下子释放出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:00.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 答得好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:02.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,终于回到平时的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:05.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 今天有两个本家的执事在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:10.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能毫无准备地从这里逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:12.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,准备？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:35.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦去浜松町方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:38.32,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,晚饭已经备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:43.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:44.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:46.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我在看烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,至少让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:50.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:06:59.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,讲笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:05.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:16.76,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜同学她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可能已经到附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原学姐你就呆在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:30.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,您拨打的电话不在服务区或已关机 无法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:32.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:34.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为人太多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:37.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说我的手机太旧了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:38.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:41.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘 你是想去烟火大会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因为交通管制 这附近是塞车了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,大概赶不上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:50.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,赶不上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可早坂都帮我到这一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:58.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我总是这么惨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:02.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:03.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:06.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的路程我靠自己走过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:14.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心啊 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:15.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:30.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我们约在竹芝码头见面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:32.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,大路上人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:35.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,抄近道的话说不定能勉强赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能见到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:45.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个我照顾的学弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:49.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个愿意跟我交朋友的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个喜欢上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:59.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我的生活 被他们所包围
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:05.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是能和我喜欢的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:08.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一起眺望那场烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那该有多么幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:13.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那该有多么美好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:16.61,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这个暑假我的脑海中充斥着这些想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:18.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这个夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:24.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我不奢求什么恋情与爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以至少让我和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,…已经结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:46.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,请您在离开时带走垃圾与食品饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:48.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:53.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的烟火大会已经结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:10:01.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,请您在离开时带走垃圾与食品饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:04.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:10.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没有神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,他们有好好享受烟火了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:23.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要是那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:28.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我只从大楼缝隙间看到了烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但那么大的烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:35.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,他们看到的烟火一定很美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:41.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,大家能高兴 我就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:53.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想看啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:56.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,烟火…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:10:59.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:04.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那我带去你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:07.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:10.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 四宫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:13.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那么想看的话我就让你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:18.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:23.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说「读出四宫的想法然后找到四宫」的游戏吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:28.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和平时那些比起来 这个简单一百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:35.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:39.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 车我弄来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:41.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,又是那个小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都坐上去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:51.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:02.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,司机 顺着这条路上高速
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:04.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,从东京湾跨海隧道去海萤岛那边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,有一场前几天因为大雨延期的烟火大会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:11.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:12.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在千叶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:16.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,木更津的烟火大会到8点半才结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:20.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,还有20分钟能到千叶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:23.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 但是值得挑战一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:26.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会让四宫看到烟火的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微加速一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不要告诉公司哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:37.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊这个帅呆了的司机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:46.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊 保佑我们一定赶上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:53.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 完全看不见外面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,东京湾跨海隧道从海里经过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,当然看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:12:59.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海萤岛停车站的路牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:01.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要到地面上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要赶上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:05.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要赶上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:12.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要赶上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都看向烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:49.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法从你的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:59.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,移开视线
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:04.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,心跳声太大了 已经
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:17.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,听不见烟火的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,新学期第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:28.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都带着心中的忧愁和期待回到日常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:33.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在什么事都没能发生的漫长暑假的最后
