Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:45.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这个男人回想这些过程
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:48.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那我带去你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:53.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,后悔得想死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:59.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说「读出四宫的想法然后找到四宫」的游戏吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:02.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,羞耻羞耻羞耻羞耻羞耻羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:03.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这太羞耻了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,黑历史
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:14.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,经过了大半的暑假都不能见到辉夜的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:17.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白银在烟火大会那天 遇到了辉夜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:20.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白银的情绪断崖式上升
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:26.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,被高涨的情绪支配说出了很多羞耻的名言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.03,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,那我带去你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:28.32,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说「读出四宫的想法然后找到四宫」的游戏吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:31.59,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,和平时那些比起来 这个简单一百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:35.02,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 但是值得挑战一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:38.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,出自 白银御行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:44.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在今后十几年想起来都会苦闷难堪的黑历史
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:48.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果现在和四宫见面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:52.61,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:55.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但你那天的话怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:58.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可以说非常自我陶醉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:03.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 真是羞耻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:06.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:09.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这学期也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:11.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？嗯…藤原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:13.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:27.34,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(50,0)\bord10\3c&HF5EEEF&\c&HA5558D&\b1}瞥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,装作没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:33.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,已经认为我羞耻到不忍直视的地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫 之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.01,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(50,0)\bord10\3c&HF5EEEF&\c&HA5558D&\b1}瞥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:47.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真的搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.50,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有好多灰尘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:51.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得我羞耻到和我绝交了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:55.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 辉夜的确是在回避白银
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:57.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这绝不是恶意的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:16:59.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说 相反
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:03.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这是害羞和紧张引起的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:07.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,通俗来说是 喜欢的逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:11.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我避开了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:18.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不就像是说我很在意会长嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:22.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,搭话吧 像暑假之前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:25.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要重建四宫的信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:28.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,自然的 开朗的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:32.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 先普通的打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:41.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,行进路线连成直线的两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:44.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一定可以开始对话的展开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:47.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:04.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同学 要先扫地才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:06.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这么多灰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:13.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好难搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我负责这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:18.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人重整旗鼓再次挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:21.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然而结果还是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:26.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 接近了更没办法直视会长的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:29.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用什么表情和四宫搭话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:32.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都差一点的相互错过的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:37.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像是空中对战的两架战斗机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:41.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是两次都错过了实在太不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:42.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:48.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 会长在害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:52.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就没有必要害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:54.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我很冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.97,0:18:55.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:58.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,下次绝对要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:00.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:13.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,星号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:19.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同学 你在把我当傻子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:22.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,请认真打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:25.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这游戏到底是什么规则
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:27.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,必须说话打破误会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:29.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:32.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 不应该是星号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:33.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:38.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是Delta啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:45.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 连你也来捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:47.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我干什么了吗我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:51.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你什么都不懂啊石上君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:53.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么一上来就这么鄙视我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:56.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,石上 我有那么滑稽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:57.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,连会长都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:04.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 虽然不知道怎么回事我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:06.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,石上坠机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:09.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪石上君碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同学也别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:17.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:19.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原坠机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:23.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才开始到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:26.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我躲着她很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:29.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是连四宫也这么来来回回好几次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.88,0:20:32.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,难道她在在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:39.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我要冷静 闭上眼睛就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:44.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我的行为并不是那么羞耻 而是特别帅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:47.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白银重新站起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:48.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,下一次 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:50.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,下次要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:07.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我…有话一定要和会长说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:10.98,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 烟火大会那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:17.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要说 对他说谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:24.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:28.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 烟火大会那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:33.79,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,羞耻羞耻羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是羞耻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:36.23,Kaguya_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,羞耻和疼同音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:41.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:43.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白银坠机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.71,0:21:46.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长我有话对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:50.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:52.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 会长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:56.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样回到了日常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:21:58.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,第二学期开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:11.97,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君と私　きっと今同じ気持ちだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:11.97,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}你和我 现在一定怀着同样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:34.50,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君から笑いかけてくれたなら　天使でいられるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:34.50,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}只要有你的微笑 我就还能如天使一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:40.79,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}気付いたの　試されてる　意地悪な駆け引きで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:40.79,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}已经注意到我在用坏心眼的谋略考验他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:43.59,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}後にはもう引けないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:43.60,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}已经不能退缩了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.76,0:22:46.55,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}仕掛けてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.76,0:22:46.55,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}让我给你设下圈套吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:53.68,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}さあ　掛かってみせて　戸惑ってみせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:53.68,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}来吧 掉进陷阱吧 不知所措吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:23:03.78,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}そして最後に伝えてみせて　好きだって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:23:03.78,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}然后在最后说出那句喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:11.45,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君と私　どんな風に恋するの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:11.45,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}你和我 将会怎样相恋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:15.33,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}探る RELATION
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:15.33,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}去探索 RELATION
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:22.96,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}余裕なんてないよ　見つめられる度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:22.96,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}每次被你注视 我一点都不从容哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.09,0:23:26.76,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}いつも震えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.09,0:23:26.76,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}我总是会颤抖着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:33.60,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}素直じゃない私を連れ出して！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:33.60,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}请带走这样不坦率的我！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:38.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱头脑战 这是无法坦诚相待的男女的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.85,0:23:40.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,心中无法说出口的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:45.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天他们也在期盼被告白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.31,0:23:48.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定让你说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:52.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「喜欢」
